{"title":"2020-02-01","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>そういえばキラ率が上がるとか書いてたけど、結局ドッコラー一つしかキラしなかったな。たぶん。</p>\n<p>また何かやらかしてるんとちゃうん？</p>\n<hr>\n<p>肺炎は嫌だけど、EX レイドもあるし駅前出撃して 98！今日は駅中には怪しげな集団がいっぱいいたけど、駅から離れるとすっかりトレイナーも疎ら。</p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a><a href=\"img/2020/2020-02-01/20200201-163626-Screenshot_20200201-163626.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-02-01/20200201-163626-Screenshot_20200201-163626.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n</h2>\n<p>本日のゼロ</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-02-01/20200131-194559-Screenshot_20200131-194559.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-02-01/20200131-194559-Screenshot_20200131-194559.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2020-02-01T19:22:32","published":"2020-02-01T19:22:32"}